Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.71,0:00:07.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks forward to the lunch break between courses. Is not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:11.58,Signs,,0,0,0,,But don't try to eat in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.24,0:00:15.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,It is very dangerous to choke.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.11,0:00:20.73,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The answer to the riddle:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The secret of the heart is the miracle of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:25.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta is desperate,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as memories haunt the young detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.39,0:00:28.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.81,0:00:30.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:32.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.90,Signs,,0,0,0,,Teitan Elementary School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.52,0:02:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, everybody, dig in!\NI don't want to see any picky eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A teenage boy eating\Nwith grade-school kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Personally,\NI'm enjoying the experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.79,0:02:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Growing up in the States, everybody\Nhelped themselves at the school cafeteria,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I usually ended up\Neating alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's intriguing how Japanese schools\Nfoster a sense of community.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:45.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, this was fun\Nthe first time around...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mitsuhiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nyou left your carrots again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm just saving\Nthem for last!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:55.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's always somebody who picks out\Nthe vegetables he doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:02.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's always a dumb guy who brags\Nabout being the fastest eater in class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:04.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Of course, in this class,\Nit's always...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray! I'm number one!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.62,0:03:09.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He beat Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},\NI'm not feeling too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I go down\Nto the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:32.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,encoded by Ruffy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:32.35,Signs,,0,0,0,,encoded by Ruffy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} left most\Nof his lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's on a diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!\NYou know him and food!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nhasn't played with us for a couple of days...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He's been going\Nstraight home after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe an upperclassman\Nis bullying him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Genta's not the kind\Nof guy who'd get bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even if he was,\Nhe'd be safer sticking with us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.38,0:04:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a problem\Nwith his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone in\Nhis family is gravely ill,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or his parents\Nare fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we can't do anything\Nabout death or divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}S-Sensei{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.86,0:04:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents are fine!\NThey're still happily running their liquor store!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.74,0:04:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was worried, so I dropped by\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s house yesterday to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it sounds like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nis afraid of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His parents told me he was shivering\Ninside his futon the moment he got home...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is he scared of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:05.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold it, Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nbehind our backs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.83,0:05:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you practicing\Nto become a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.83,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! You skipped lunch\Nto slim down for ninjutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.38,0:05:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this cool ninja flick\Nthe other day and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why were you shivering\Nunder the covers at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe you had a nightmare about\Nbeing attacked by a bloody samurai,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.47,0:05:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and you're training to\Nfight your imaginary enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a nightmare!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.19,0:05:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I... The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My life is in danger!\NA hitman's out to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hitman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would a hitman want\Nto kill an elementary school kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it was dumb\Nto tell you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.22,0:06:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Ntell us the whole story!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I won't laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was walking through that\Ntunnel under the train tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when I heard these\Nfootsteps behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see\Nanything in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but when I stopped, he'd stop,\Nand when I ran, he ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:39.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably just the echo of your\Nfootsteps against the tunnel wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, somebody pushed me\Ndown the stairs on the overpass,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and yesterday a motorbike\Nran a red light and almost hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was just coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A big bolt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where could it\Nhave fallen from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:20.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's from that\Ndepartment store sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bolt just happened\Nto rust out, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just having a bad day!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.96,0:07:30.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, maybe you should go to a shrine\Nand have them do a purifying ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... This was more\Nthan just luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cord on this neon sign\Nwas cut with a sharp object.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone deliberately cut it before\Nloosening the bolt, to drop the sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:50.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's true, maybe it was just a crazy guy\Nattacking anybody who passed by...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I think there\Nwas a specific target.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.91,0:07:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:08:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this the Kamen Yaiba capsule machine\NGenta's always drooling over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then he really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Looks like Genta's life\Nreally {\i1}is{\i0} in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd better tell us\Neverything, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:21.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you a target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw the serial snatcher?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crook who's been snatching bags\Nfrom old people and unsuspecting women?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:48.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... About a week later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see the wanted\Nposters until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They asked where I'd seen\Nthe guy on the posters,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and by that time I'd forgotten\Nwhere I saw the guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then I saw a guy\Nwho saw the snatcher with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saw him with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.44,0:09:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five days ago, the snatcher\Nattacked a woman by my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I dropped by\Nthe crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:18.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw\Nhim in the crowd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blond guy who was near me\Nwhen I saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed him by the hand\Nand took him to the nearest cop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the guy said he didn't\Nremember me or the snatcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure\Nhe was the same guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When I saw the snatcher,\NI think that guy was sitting near me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he must've\Nseen the snatcher too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was really sleepy then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I swear that\Nblond guy was nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think he was there too.\NOr maybe he wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you'd get\Nsleepy after sitting down...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A movie theater...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or inside a train...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the look of things, the blond guy is probably\Nworking with the person targeting Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Why didn't you tell\Nthe police you were in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I got a phone call...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"If you say anything about me, you're dead!\NAnd your friends and family too!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you didn't\Ntell anybody until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is going\Nfrom bad to worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.07,0:10:38.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knows your phone number,\Nhe must know where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:41.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. If we went\Nto the police,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.41,0:10:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the snatcher might think\NGenta remembered something,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:46.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and there's no telling\Nwhat he'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He might even be spying\Non us this very minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember anything\Nthat might help us look for the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told the cops,\Nbut he was smoking a cigarette with his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the snatcher\Nis left-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was wearing\Na weird T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.98,0:11:12.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was black with\Na skull and numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.56,0:11:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one! That one!\NIt was just like that one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you the snatcher\Nwho's after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.03,0:11:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. He doesn't look\Nlike the guy I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the snatcher's T-shirt\Ndidn't say "1999".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "202"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you remember\Nwhere you got that T-shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:43.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A shop by the train station\Ncalled Bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!\NThe skull shirt is an original from our shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've put out a lot of versions,\Nbut I don't remember one that said "202".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What other versions are there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"1999", "HELP", "ESCAPE"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of dangerous-sounding words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You remember back in 1999,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when everyone was talking about\Nend-of-the-millennium prophecies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we\Ndid a 1999 shirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you remember any suspicious-looking\Npeople buying those T-shirts?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno. It's been a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I don't really remember\Nall our customers' faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that didn't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could try movie theaters\Nand trains!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. You can't smoke\Nin those places.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! You must've gotten sleepy\Nfrom eating too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:48.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that guy\Nwasn't eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:51.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was watching him\Nthe whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I just remember him reading\Na newspaper and smoking a cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you can remember all that,\Nbut not where you were?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't he get annoyed at you\Nfor staring at him for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, our eyes never met...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's where they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:18.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skull T-shirt\Nwith the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.31,0:13:20.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And a place where your eyes\Nwould never meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:25.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and you wouldn't attract attention\Nfor staring at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:28.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've got it, Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The very place\Nyou saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The optician's, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's where you\Nsaw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said he didn't get upset\Neven though you were staring at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't see you staring at him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he'd taken his glasses off\Nto have them fixed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But, Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never been\Nto an optician's.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's got to be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all,\Nit'd also have...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Seriously?\NI thought I'd cracked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself\Nthe modern-day Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.\NEven a genius makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't feel down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me if you remember anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:48.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where could it be?\NThe place Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} saw the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where you can stare at somebody\Nwithout getting in trouble, and also get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.58,0:14:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's school!\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} always falls asleep there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:15:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the snatcher was at our school,\Nwe'd have seen him too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, for crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never stop eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're going to put on weight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares?\NI like to snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got ice cream on your face,\NGenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you remember something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful on your way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.74,0:15:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three chicken and four liver, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:39.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm getting hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you just have\Nsome ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,French food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show some self-control!\NYou're almost home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red... White... Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?\NThat's the French flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen the colors\Nred, white and blue anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:13.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s always wearing a red bowtie,\Nwhite shirt and blue jacket...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-Is he the snatcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right.\NWould Conan do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but the colors\Nred, white and blue keep spinning in my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't forget\Nto go straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:39.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get any fatter,\Neven the piggies will laugh at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.19,0:16:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid Ayumi,\Ncalling me fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not that fat, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember!\NIt was back there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seventh floor of\Nthe building above the station...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:13.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, stop! Hold that elevator!\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which floor, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.55,0:17:19.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The s-seventh floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're that blond... guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about forgetting you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:34.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remembered where it was!\NWhere you and me saw the snatcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.11,0:17:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could be\Nlistening in on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you remember too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's talk it over\Nbefore we go to the cops,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:51.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and make sure we've got\Nour stories straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.46,0:17:55.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere safe\Nfrom other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like a restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:17:59.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:03.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I think the name he wrote\Nin our schedule book was Someda...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't knock off\Nthe accusations, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Left-handed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A T-shirt with a skull\Nand the number 202...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No wonder the police couldn't\Npin down the snatcher's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta was looking at your\Nreflection in a mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You're the kids from before!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:33.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you never got angry at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nfor staring at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:38.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he was watching you\Nin the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "202" he saw written\Non your T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was actually "SOS"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.68,0:18:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the left hand\Nwas really your right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where Genta would go that has\Na mirror in front of the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.81,0:18:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and where he could get sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the barber shop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta didn't realize you and\Nthe snatcher were the same person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.87,0:19:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because you had your hair\Nbleached while he was napping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A guy with a black hair and glasses\Nchanged into a blond guy without glasses,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Genta didn't see your clothes\Nbecause they were covered with a smock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He misremembered you\Nas two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.63,0:19:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about,\Nyou little brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:26.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an eyewitness\Nstanding right behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber who\Ndyed your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've been lucky until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As it happens,\Nthe barber doesn't watch TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the police haven't posted\Nyour picture in his neighborhood yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dyed your hair black with coloring\Nthat could be washed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:52.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you thought\Nno one would recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the police got the snatcher's fingerprints\Noff the last bag he tried to snatch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.26,0:20:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those prints match yours,\Nyou can't talk your way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-So what was this kid\Ndoing back in this neighborhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Luring you here,\Nthat's what!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We had him get ice cream on his face\Nthat looked like shaving cream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:21.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stare at the French flag, which is\Nred, white and blue like a barber pole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.65,0:20:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he stared\Nat his reflection...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,like he was looking\Nin a barber's mirror!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:32.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We knew all along\Nthat you were following us,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so we convinced Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}\Nto play dumb—no difficult task—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and lure you into a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kids think\Nyou can mess with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you doing,\Nyou old broad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.89,0:20:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're pretty dumb, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really think I'd walk all over town\Njust to lure you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NLook around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.02,0:21:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Genta bought us some time,\Nwe made a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This place is\Nswarming with cops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:12.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's how the\Nsnatcher got arrested,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:14.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the case closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't believe the words\Ncoming out of your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you really a grade-schooler,\NConan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just imitating\Nthe detectives on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:55.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A huge victory for the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:22:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.68,0:22:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're so lazy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you totally fell asleep\Nwhile the snatcher was having his hair dyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The barber said he didn't wake me up\Nbecause I looked so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess they say sleep\Nis good for growing kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.74,0:23:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you were right\Nand the criminal wasn't really left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.91,0:23:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty sure it wasn't {\i1}him{\i0},\Nsince he'd target me before Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it did shake me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.59,0:23:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't know?\NThen here's another factoid for your files.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gin is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.23,0:23:48.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:53.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}T-This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he wanted to see\Nwhat was inside this attaché case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, the key\Nis still in the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a curse.
